description: Lists all the themes in the current Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the themes that you're listing.

parameters.name: Type
parameters.description: The type of themes that you want to list. Valid options include the following: ALL (default)- Display all existing themes. CUSTOM - Display only the themes created by people using Amazon QuickSight. QUICKSIGHT - Display only the starting themes defined by Amazon QuickSight.

nested_items.name: ThemeSummaryList
nested_items.description: Information about the themes in the list.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: the display name for the theme.

nested_items.name: ThemeId
nested_items.description: The ID of the theme. This ID is unique per Amazon Web Services Region for each Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: LatestVersionNumber
nested_items.description: The latest version number for the theme.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that this theme was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The last date and time that this theme was updated.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
